      "text": "是贪婪或依赖",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 44.494,
      "time_str": "00:44.494",
      "text": "才敢说你不是不爱",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 50.508,
      "time_str": "00:50.508",
      "text": "爱才是最大的伤害",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 54.615,
      "time_str": "00:54.615",
      "text": "看似温柔的虐待",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 57.288,
      "time_str": "00:57.288",
      "text": "随你安排 我离开",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
